# Code Health Analysis

## When to use

- Analyzing overall code health of a PHP/Laravel project
- Running health checks (Pint, PHPStan, Pest pipeline)
- Scoring code quality dimensions (readability, complexity, coupling, cohesion)
- Identifying quick wins for code improvement

## Keywords

`code health quality analysis score maintainability complexity coupling cohesion`
